- "<p>\u201CIt wasn\u2019t the wind that blew down this post,\u201D observed Pencroft.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CNo,\u201D replied Gideon Spilett. \u201CThe earth has been dug up round\
  \ its foot, and it has been torn up by the hand of man.\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CBesides, the wire is broken,\u201D added Herbert, showing that the wire\
