- "<p>\u201CIs the fracture recent?\u201D asked Harding.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CYes,\u201D answered Herbert, \u201Cit has certainly been done quite lately.\u201D\
  </p>"
- "<p>\u201CTo the corral! to the corral!\u201D exclaimed the sailor.</p>"
- <p>The colonists were now half way between Granite House and the corral, having
