- "<p>\u201CLet us enter,\u201D said Cyrus Harding.</p>"
- "<p>And the engineer advanced, while his companions, keeping watch about twenty\
  \ paces behind him, were ready to fire at a moment\u2019s notice.</p>"
- <p>Harding raised the inner latch of the gate and was about to push it back, when
