- <p>Herbert, struck by a bullet, lay stretched on the ground.</p>
- <p>Chapter 7</p>
- "<p>At Herbert\u2019s cry, Pencroft, letting his gun fall, rushed towards him.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CThey have killed him!\u201D he cried. \u201CMy boy! They have killed him!\u201D\
