- "<p>\u201CBut the heart?\u201D asked Harding.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CThe heart has not been touched; if it had been, Herbert would be dead!\u201D\
  </p>"
- "<p>\u201CDead!\u201D exclaimed Pencroft, with a groan.</p>"
- <p>The sailor had only heard the last words uttered by the reporter.</p>
- "<p>\u201CNo, Pencroft,\u201D replied Cyrus Harding, \u201Cno! He is not dead. His\
