- "<p>\u201CDo not make us lose it, my friend.\u201D</p>"
- <p>Pencroft was silent, but a reaction set in, and great tears rolled down his cheeks.</p>
- <p>In the meanwhile, Gideon Spilett endeavored to collect his ideas, and proceed
