- "<p>\u201CCyrus,\u201D said he, \u201CI am not a surgeon. I am in terrible perplexity.\
  \ You must aid me with your advice, your experience!\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CTake courage, my friend,\u201D answered the engineer, pressing the reporter\u2019\
