- "<p>\u201CAm not I here?\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CTop!\u201D exclaimed Cyrus Harding.</p>"
- "<p>The animal sprang at his master\u2019s call.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CYes, Top will go,\u201D said the reporter, who had understood the engineer.</p>"
