  by all the angles, all the projections of the cavern. This light proceeded from
  an electric source, and its white color betrayed its origin. It was the sun of this
  cave, and it filled it entirely.</p>
- "<p>At a sign from Cyrus Harding the oars again plunged into the water, causing\
