- "<p>\u201CHe! an outlawed man!\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CHe!\u201D said Harding.</p>"
- "<p>At the engineer\u2019s command the boat approached this singular floating apparatus.\
  \ The boat touched the left side, from which escaped a ray of light through a thick\
