- "<p>\u201CThe ?Nautilus\u2019?\u201D said the captain, with a faint smile.</p>"
- "<p>\u201CThe ?Nautilus.\u201C</p>"
- "<p>\u201CBut do you?do you know who I am?\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CI do.\u201D</p>"
- "<p>\u201CIt is nevertheless many years since I have held any communication with\
