  \ the fugitives, engulfed in that frightful whirlpool, found their death at the\
  \ bottom of the abyss. He was unaware that the Frenchman and his two companions\
  \ had been miraculously cast on shore, that the fishermen of the Lofoten Islands\
  \ had rendered them assistance, and that the professor, on his return to France,\
  \ had published that work in which seven months of the strange and eventful navigation\
